It should be the power of // 2. int scale = 1; while (o.outWidth / scale / 2 >= REQUIRED_SIZE && o.outHeight / scale / 2 >= REQUIRED_SIZE) scale *= 2; // Decode with inSampleSize BitmapFactory.Options o2 = new BitmapFactory.Options(); o2.inSampleSize = scale; return BitmapFactory.decodeFile(path, o2); } catch (Throwable e) { e.printStackTrace(); } return null; } public String getAbsolutePath(Uri uri) { String[] projection = { MediaColumns.DATA }; Cursor cursor = managedQuery(uri, projection, null, null, null); if (cursor != null) { int column_index = cursor.getColumnIndexOrThrow(MediaColumns.DATA); cursor.moveToFirst(); return cursor.getString(column_index); } else return null; }
